name: Anicons - 3D icons
description:
Anicons is a pack of stylish and playful 3D icons that can be used instantly in your projects. The pack consists of 30 high-res, well-organized and commonly-used icons that can be customized easily. 


The full pack includes:

  • 30 front view of 3D icons
  • Figma, PNG, and C4D files included
  • 4000*4000px resolution
  • Example screens
  • FREE future updates


You can change the color, layers, and gloss effect of the icons as per your requirement, and get Figma, PNG, and CD4 files.
